{"tid":1298202,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[你成日好攰] 統計一下香港有幾多人有慢性疲勞綜合症症狀 (Chronic Fatigue Syndrome)","createTime":"2019-07-08T21:35:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T19:55:52.000Z","uid":162988,"like":66,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b0922a646c92c9974fbcb4876543c310c761397c","tid":1298202,"uid":162988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T21:35:13.000Z","msg":"你有冇以下症狀：<br />\n1. 訓完起身好攰<br />\n2. 全身肌肉或關節痛<br />\n3. 頭痛<br />\n4. 唔可以運動太耐，否則更加攰<br />\n5. 或呢個網講既症狀：<a href=\"https://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/chronic-fatigue-syndrome/symptoms-causes/syc-20360490\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mayoclinic.org%2Fdiseases-conditions%2Fchronic-fatigue-syndrome%2Fsymptoms-causes%2Fsyc-20360490&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dgmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=2181b868\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/chronic-fatigue-syndrome/symptoms-causes/syc-20360490</a><br />\n<br />\n其實呢個問題係外國好多人講，但係華人好少講，香港好多醫生都唔承認有呢個病既存在，因為到今日仲未搵到個原因<br />\n<br />\n外國亦都有人抗議醫學界忽略呢個問題，以致好多好少錢放入去研究呢個病<br />\n<br />\n外國亦都有一d好extreme既病例，有d人直情攰到訓左係床好多日都起唔到身，好似下面條片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Fb3yp4uJhq0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFb3yp4uJhq0&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dgmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=950fc3c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Fb3yp4uJhq0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果你有以上一個或幾個症狀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我好精神鬼有病<br />\n<br />\n利申：<br />\n我自己本身診斷有焦慮症<br />\n1. 成日訓完起身都好攰，果種攰係幾辛苦<br />\n2. 有失真症Derealization，即係覺得周圍d野好假<br />\n3. 有其實身心症狀，例如胃脹，心悸等"},{"pid":"9eb9f931129adf60bf29f7ba5b13a8de07017e59","tid":1298202,"uid":162988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T21:39:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b38e4e5ef479537f43e3b207dea8628f06531407","tid":1298202,"uid":243380,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T21:41:59.000Z","msg":"聽起黎一個symptom 都冇反而係異類"},{"pid":"c8c2714d10148130776cf5ac6c3bbf8ed8011cc2","tid":1298202,"uid":162988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T21:53:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca5d66d0f575f7236fe97869342aa184fe6be111","tid":1298202,"uid":156618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T22:23:52.000Z","msg":"未睇片，係咪冇解決方法？"},{"pid":"8b9d2c0569159e3e89960c8e2c0edfdf11eb1d5c","tid":1298202,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:07:29.000Z","msg":"以前有1，4家陣可能都有<br />\n<br />\n中醫病友fb gp<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/954306168239427/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F954306168239427%2F&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dgmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=cdc4ac13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/954306168239427/</a><br />\n中醫病友tg gp<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/E38pyBRjAYZAparanxCZUA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FE38pyBRjAYZAparanxCZUA&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dgmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=fe76ba4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/E38pyBRjAYZAparanxCZUA</a><br />\n<br />\n男，20-25歲,病左5年,輕度肥胖<br />\n睇過13個醫師，計埋好快放棄嘅至少20<br />\n<br />\n症狀：疲倦,不精神,四肢無力,手：愈近末梢，愈少力。切兩個橙好攰，要休息。合上眼後指頭不太能分辨尖/頓。乏力以手為主，職業治療檢查出我手小肌肉做重複性動作好快攰。腳：行約1小時覺攰，要休息。全身：試過拎3.5kg行10分鐘，超攰。有時覺肚向下the。有時膝痛。有手腳心汗。腳板脫皮，病發後腳掌較以前闊，要買加加闊版鞋。<br />\n無覺得凍/熱。大小便正常。無失眠。無骨傷史。無地貧。<br />\n<br />\n病因：我估5-8年前，食太多龜苓膏涼茶搞到成日腹瀉，之後個人慢慢愈來愈攰<br />\n<br />\n近一年處方：<a href=\"https://photos.app.goo.gl/9MZZuLHDzs1esvbA6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotos.app.goo.gl%2F9MZZuLHDzs1esvbA6&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dgmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=0603b6ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://photos.app.goo.gl/9MZZuLHDzs1esvbA6</a><br />\n<br />\n近日處方有十全大補、黃精、杞子，每次飲完都微微有力，疑整體藥量太少/熟地太少（見張鍚純開過４兩）/沖劑無力<br />\n<br />\n睇過既醫師:<br />\n黃志忠 客座副教授 中大中醫專科診所暨臨床教硏中心<br />\n莫飛智 師從鄧鐵濤 前港大助理教授 中大客座副教授<br />\n馬劍穎（睇過幾次放棄） 一級講師 浸大中醫藥診所<br />\n李廣冀 遠志中醫<br />\n商海峰 林鐵志 專科門診 博愛醫院-香港中文大學中醫教研中心(元朗)<br />\n葉嘉禮 陸葉中醫診所<br />\n仲有街邊藥房中醫唔打出黎<br />\n<br />\n西醫:睇過腦神經內科,等緊內科神經傳導檢查。照過胸背x光。有脂肪肝。 肝酵素高。<br />\n<br />\n聯絡方法：<br />\nFb messager <a href=\"https://m.me/seek.chinesemedicine.1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.me%2Fseek.chinesemedicine.1&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dgmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=11ce608c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.me/seek.chinesemedicine.1</a><br />\nTg<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Usernamennn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FUsernamennn&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dgmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=f66af341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Usernamennn</a>"},{"pid":"2c659f2f85cb665a7238ca9f198972f4edf179c1","tid":1298202,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:09:33.000Z","msg":"試過中醫未，有中醫學生介紹黃斌 張清苓"},{"pid":"2534d3ac12686d6cd35fd68ee381d1577541d47f","tid":1298202,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:42:18.000Z","msg":"係香港會當為精神問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3de63e371f9d338ea7b20b38ad1e0c545f1bcd","tid":1298202,"uid":162988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:04:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90ee924e31e710da9a59f27e025553b55be75b2c","tid":1298202,"uid":266231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:06:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9609542f7144444fdf91fed66d5b38df916f6e2","tid":1298202,"uid":162988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2534d3ac12686d6cd35fd68ee381d1577541d47f","tid":1298202,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:42:18.000Z","msg":"係香港會當為精神問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:13:39.000Z","msg":"係外國好多醫生都會咁覺得，佢地check唔到生理上有咩事就即刻判斷個病人係精神問題"},{"pid":"2ad1ab9d21806b8494af327c86ee84c27c689bab","tid":1298202,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:14:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f923a613a21a69bfd7a108b736425e1304b9ecb","tid":1298202,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:14:50.000Z","msg":"又係呢啲作個名既病"},{"pid":"b78ec3e2ee7c26b6d47895a6e60c7ed23674b904","tid":1298202,"uid":162988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:23:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"63caef342f5a802e1ab89f13cc92e40f39b8eadf","tid":1298202,"uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T03:55:26.000Z","msg":"Chronic fatigue syndrome 好似係指肉體上既疲勞，而唔係精神上既疲勞？"},{"pid":"a4329e871fb5c40cd4478378ff7a624f4b15d7ac","tid":1298202,"uid":85110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:30:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f40fd56522291c9d6aa424422c11523be9d0573","tid":1298202,"uid":162988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:43:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8a1fd021c18d314a79fe5558af93a9c83ff77df","tid":1298202,"uid":16087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:46:10.000Z","msg":"我有時都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得係自己心理既諗法影響到生理<br />\n好似我咁<br />\n呢排唔太鐘意出街，一出街就攰想返歸<br />\n但去打波又好精神唔攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c93e7fd438b6c75cde9325936bb7a40a4f2851f","tid":1298202,"uid":48390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:53:27.000Z","msg":"成日好攰，少少郁動就心跳快，心悸，容易緊張，突然好似透唔到氣，　訓得唔好，腳汗多<br />\n<br />\n試過睇好幾個醫生，做過身體檢查，個個都話我冇事<br />\n<br />\n直到有次遇到個好醫生傾左半個鐘，其實根本係大壓力排解唔到，影響到身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfbf504492544a5106108a94cb33734663edc7ad","tid":1298202,"uid":162988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:37:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17d520ee8effd6cecb2d7772a26d31fefab62ceb","tid":1298202,"uid":162988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:52:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"820a36f6f575adbd72578a97670620b9e1e29ec4","tid":1298202,"uid":162988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T12:11:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa8ae9ef308b94f76494425edf0369a02dd55e2a","tid":1298202,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:57:40.000Z","msg":"你會唔會對眼成日失焦?"},{"pid":"0954fb04553f0f9cddbc2974efb12a388f1b57a7","tid":1298202,"uid":162988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa8ae9ef308b94f76494425edf0369a02dd55e2a","tid":1298202,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:57:40.000Z","msg":"你會唔會對眼成日失焦?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:17:36.000Z","msg":"我會，醫生話係焦慮症問題"},{"pid":"0dd6163583f44dffae465373521729f5b626a07a","tid":1298202,"uid":162988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:48:26.000Z","msg":"推"}]}